      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-ExportFBXfromMudbox\">Export FBX from Mudbox</h3><p>Before you start sculpting, export your Fbx from Mudbox.</p><h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-ExportanOpenEXRfromMudbox\">Export an OpenEXR from Mudbox</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"394\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561195&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=1004\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/mudbox_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561195&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1137\" data-width=\"446\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540761\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mudbox_extractTextureMaps.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"110f2014-8bcd-4391-91b8-7293b35a099b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561195&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=1137 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561195&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=1004 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-ExportaPTexfromMudbox\">Export a PTex from Mudbox</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"394\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=1010\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/mudbox_ptex_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1146\" data-width=\"447\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540767\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mudbox_ptex_extractTextureMaps.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9f9ec12f-24df-4704-9c9b-6d7c6e8489b0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=1146 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_extractTextureMaps.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=1010 1x\"></span><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-ImportFBXandAddSubdivScheme\">Import FBX and Add Subdiv Scheme</h3><ul><li><p>Import the FBX you just exported from Mudbox.  For its shape node, add <strong>Attributes|RenderMan|Subdiv Scheme:</strong></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/subdivScheme.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561195&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/subdivScheme.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561195&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"119\" data-width=\"367\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540758\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"subdivScheme.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"572c463e-8f1e-4889-a884-b06c3acbad6c\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-AssignDisplacementShader(UVTexture)\">Assign Displacement Shader (UV Texture)</h3><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>PxrTexture</strong> node. Set the Filename to your exported Muxbox EXR map. Keep all parameters at their defaults.</p></li><li><p>Create <strong> PxrDispTransform</strong> node. Set Displacement Type to <strong>Mudbox Vector</strong> and Vector Space to <strong>Tangent</strong>.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"985\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=350\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/mudbox_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"350\" data-width=\"442\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540764\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mudbox_PxrDispTransform.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1e4a12fa-95eb-4314-a428-e3c30e8e0f27\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=350 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=350 1x\"></span><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>PxrDisplace</strong> node (this is the displacement shader that actually displaces your surface).</p></li><li><p>Connect PxrTexture's output Result RGB to PxrDispTransform's Disp Vector.</p></li><li><p>Connect PxrDispTransform's Result XYZ to PxrDisplace's Disp Vector. Your graph should look like this:</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-AssignDisplacementShader(PTex)\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=325\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540841\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"vectorDispGraph.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"30850a1d-144b-46d0-9b1e-341d080e40b8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=968&amp;height=394 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=325 1x\"></span>Assign Displacement Shader (PTex)</h3><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>PxrPtexture</strong> node. Set the Filename to your exported Muxbox ptx map. Keep all parameters at their defaults.</p></li><li><p>Create <strong> PxrDispTransform</strong> node. Set Displacement Type to <strong>Mudbox Vector</strong> and Vector Space to <strong>World</strong>.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"482\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=437&amp;height=270\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/mudbox_ptex_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"270\" data-width=\"437\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540770\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mudbox_ptex_PxrDispTransform.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bf8302e4-db20-439c-ae49-0ec90e49da0c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=437&amp;height=270 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561530&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=437&amp;height=270 1x\"></span><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>PxrDisplace</strong> node (this is the displacement shader that actually displaces your surface).</p></li><li><p>Connect PxrTexture's output Result RGB to PxrDispTransform's Disp Vector.</p></li><li><p>Connect PxrDispTransform's Result XYZ to PxrDisplace's Disp Vector. Your graph should look like this:</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"578\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561721&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=578&amp;height=247\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/mudbox_ptex_vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561721&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"356\" data-width=\"830\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540773\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mudbox_ptex_vectorDispGraph.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"56316a4f-c522-4172-a042-ffdec3a36d36\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561721&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=830&amp;height=356 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561721&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=578&amp;height=247 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"MudboxVectorDisplacement-Render\">Render</h3><ul><li><p>Add <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=RFM24&amp;title=PxrSurface\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrSurface</a>, assign it to the model and add some <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544541369/Lighting+in+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541369\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">lights</a>, set the displacement bound appropriately, and render! <br/><em>Toad King created created by Craig Barr, Autodesk Media and Entertainment.</em><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"mudbox_ptex_toadKing.jpg\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_toadKing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561194&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540737/mudbox_ptex_toadKing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561194&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540755\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mudbox_ptex_toadKing.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540737\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"480e659a-7ab6-4d58-bd21-d02f20c5c924\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_toadKing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561194&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540737/mudbox_ptex_toadKing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431561194&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 1x\"></span><p> <br/><br/></p><p><br/><br/><br/></p></li></ul>"
    }
